074    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T> & VersionedTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<?, ? extends DeleteCommand<?>, ?>> T delete(
075            final T request, final long version, final TQuery deleteDsl) {
076        T deleteRequest = request;
077        for (ExpansionPath<?> expansionPath : deleteDsl.expansionPaths()) {
078            deleteRequest = (T) deleteRequest.addExpand(expansionPath.toSphereExpand());
079        }
080        request.withVersion(version);
081        return deleteRequest;
082    }

084    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T> & VersionedTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<?, ? extends DeleteCommand<?>, ?>> T delete(
085            final T request, final long version, final Supplier<TQuery> createDelete,
086            final Function<TQuery, TQuery> deleteDsl) {
087        MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<?, ? extends DeleteCommand<?>, ?> delete = deleteDsl.apply(createDelete.get());
088        return delete(request, version, delete);
089    }

091    public <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T> & VersionedTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<?, ? extends DeleteCommand<?>, ?>> T with(
092            final Function<ProjectApiRoot, T> request, final long version, final Supplier<TQuery> createDeleteDsl,
093            final Function<TQuery, TQuery> deleteDsl) {
094        MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<?, ? extends DeleteCommand<?>, ?> delete = deleteDsl
095                .apply(createDeleteDsl.get());
096        return delete(request.apply(apiRoot), version, delete);
097    }
